  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"item-attunement\"><p><em>(Requires attunement by a creature. The properties of this item are affixed to a set of armor.)</em></p></div><p><em>This item is a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3]{locus} and can be combined with other <strong>Loci </strong>per the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3.JournalEntryPage.zI0VWGKnYZqz6sKd]{Combining Loci} rules.</em></p><p>These fuzzy black threads are nearly impossible to cut and make it difficult to distinguish the shape of anything they are draped upon.</p><p>While attuned the threads merges magically merges with <strong>armor</strong> of your choice. This can be done during a short or long rest, requires 10 minutes to complete and it upon completion the item takes on a dark coloring and if the material has fabric than it because frayed. Once completed, the item becomes magical.</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Whenever the attuned creature has temporary hit points, treat them as if they are similar to the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.2aLblO17IpvCGu64]{Armor of Agathys} if they are removed. The damage dealt in this way is necrotic damage.</p>",
